## Local frontend env (Vite)
## Copy this file to `.env.local` (do NOT commit `.env.local`) and adjust as needed.
## This URL is used for ALL API requests across the frontend.
##
## Local backend:
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000

##
## Same machine, different IP (e.g. frontend at 192.168.1.11:5173, backend on same host):
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://192.168.1.11:3000

##
## Remote backend example:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://16.112.146.20:3000
























